        <div class="section-title">Key Projects & Impact</div>
        <ul class="grid-main">
            <li>
                <span class="proj-title">Core Shift ML Model</span>
                <p>Developed a machine learning model analyzing past schedules to automatically generate optimized employee schedules for the upcoming week, significantly improving operational efficiency.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="proj-title">AI Forecast & Optimization</span>
                <p>Designed and implemented an AI/ML and mathematical optimization solution to enhance workforce forecasting accuracy and scheduling efficiency within Altametrics, predicting labor hours and optimizing staffing with business constraints.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="proj-title">Auto Skill Upgrade AI</span>
                <p>Engineered an AI-based solution that evaluates employee scheduled hours, recommending skill level upgrades to managers based on time spent on specific job codes.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="proj-title">Position Guide Labor Model</span>
                <p>Created a labor percentage model that schedules employees based on historical labor cost trends, incorporating visual dashboards and graphs for analyzing shifts, labor percentages, and weekly scheduling insights.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="proj-title">Smart Clock Face ID</span>
                <p>Developed a secure, AI-driven Face ID time clock for contactless attendance and compliance, enhancing security and streamlining check-ins.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="proj-title">eRestaurant UI/Dashboards</span>
                <p>Enhanced the eRestaurant product by redesigning user interfaces for HR, Timekeeping, Labor, Payroll, and Scheduling modules, adding interactive dashboards for business insights and cost savings.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="proj-title">Mobile App Enhancements</span>
                <p>Improved Altametrics DAR, Schedule, and Clock mobile applications by integrating new features based on user feedback, boosting business productivity.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="proj-title">Time Loss & Labor Dashboard</span>
                <p>Developed an advanced dashboard tool capable of identifying operational inefficiencies, leading to potential savings of up to $1,000 per week for franchisees.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="proj-title">Catalog Management System</span>
                <p>Implemented API automation for SKU listing and ensured product data consistency across multiple online marketplaces, reducing catalog errors by 30%.</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
